libdivsufsort (2.0.1-2) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Changed section from science to libs
  * Changed watch urls to GitHub, hoping that upstream becomes active again.
  * The -dev package now depends on the library (Closes: #794729)
  * Minor changes include: added symbols file, cleaner rules/install/docs/dirs,
    removed git-orig-source script, fixed make clean target, updated description
  * Introduced multi-arch support:
    Added Multi-Arch: same and Pre-Depends: ${misc:Pre-Depends}
    Patched upstream cmake files, so all files are installed into their proper,
    architecture-dependent directories. (Thanks to Tomasz for the patch.)

